        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 3 at 8:26PM CDT until June 3 at 9:15PM CDT by NWS Chicago IL</headline>
        <description>At 825 PM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from near Shannon to near Dixon to near Woodhaven Lakes,
moving northeast at 50 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Oregon, Polo, Baileyville, Amboy, Lindenwood, Grand Detour, West
Brooklyn, Ashton, Kings, Chana, Franklin Grove, Hillcrest, Harmon,
Nachusa, Woodland Shores, Steward, Stillman Valley, Byron, Leaf
River, Nelson, Eldena, Compton, Mount Morris, Woosung, and Davis
Junction.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
